      "span_text": "However, it was an open problem to find the 'most efficient' way of tiling R d (in some well defined geometric sense of 'efficient'). [CITATION_2] gives a randomized algorithm outputting the shape of the cell so that the entire space is fully covered and no two cells overlap (thus, it is a tiling) and each cell corresponds to one grid point."
